PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,FA boy, aged 13, has died after being
OL,8,Fpulled from the water at London's
OL,9,FRoyal Victoria Dock.
OL,11,FITV News London understands the
OL,12,Fteenager was playing football with
OL,13,Fschool friends on a small beach.
OL,15,FAn eyewitness, who asked not to be
OL,16,Fidentified, told ITV News London the
OL,17,Fball went into the water and the boy
OL,18,Fswam after it, but got into difficulty
OL,19,Fand disappeared below the surface.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,FThe witness said the boy's friends
OL,8,Fcalled police and emergency services
OL,9,Farrived within ten minutes.
OL,11,FA police helicopter found the child
OL,12,Fbut by the time he was pulled from the
OL,13,Fwater he could not be revived.
OL,15,FThere were no other people reported in
OL,16,Fthe water or other reported injuries.
OL,18,FA sign on the edge of the dock says
OL,19,F"No swimming" but the letters are
OL,20,Fabout two inches tall and hard to read
OL,21,Ffrom the beach.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,FOne nearby business was so concerned
OL,8,Fabout the lack of signs it put up a
OL,9,Fhandwritten warning poster saying:
OL,10,F"Danger. Deep water" and another
OL,11,Fillustrating the sudden drop in depth.
OL,13,FThe Mayor of London, Sadiq Khan, said:
OL,14,F"My heart goes out to the family and
OL,15,Floved ones of the child who has
OL,16,Ftragically drowned, and my thoughts
OL,17,Fare with all those affected at this
OL,18,Fdifficult time.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,F"I have asked Royal Docks officials to
OL,8,Fensure the family receives all support
OL,9,Favailable to them, and remain in touch
OL,10,Fwith the Met while they investigate
OL,11,Fthe circumstances that led to this
OL,12,Fdevastating incident."
OL,14,FA statement from Royal Docks Waterways
OL,15,Fadded: "Royal Docks Waterways is
OL,16,Fdeeply saddened to learn of the death
OL,17,Fof a young person following an
OL,18,Fincident in the water last night.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,F"Our thoughts are with the family and
OL,8,Ffriends of those involved at this
OL,9,Fextremely difficult time.
OL,11,F"Royal Docks Waterways will continue
OL,12,Fto work with relevant partners to
OL,13,Fensure the safety messaging around the
OL,14,Fdocks is as clear as possible."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
