OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,FDetective Superintendent Scott Ware,
OL,8,Fwho leads public protection in north
OL,9,Feast London, said: "Our thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with the boy's family and loved
OL,11,Fones as they come to terms with this
OL,12,Ftragedy. We kindly ask that their
OL,13,Fprivacy is respected.
OL,15,F"We also make a plea to the public to
OL,16,Favoid speculation and refrain from
OL,17,Fsharing distressing material online
OL,18,Fout of respect for the family and to
OL,19,Fpreserve the investigation.
OL,26,@qD@TOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,F"Our sincere thanks go to the
OL,8,Femergency services and partner
OL,9,Fagencies involved in the search-and-
OL,10,Frecovery efforts this evening, as well
OL,11,Fas members of the public who offered
OL,12,Fassistance and support.
OL,14,F"This incident is now being
OL,15,Finvestigated on behalf of the coroner
OL,16,Fand inquiries remain ongoing to
OL,17,Festablish the full circumstances of
OL,18,Fwhat happened."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,FA London Ambulance Service
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "We were called at
OL,9,F4.07pm on Monday June 29 to reports of
OL,10,Fa person in the water at Dock Road,
OL,11,FSilvertown.
OL,13,F"We sent resources to the scene
OL,14,Fincluding an ambulance crew, an
OL,15,Fincident response officer and
OL,16,Fparamedics from our hazardous area
OL,17,Fresponse team (HART). We also
OL,18,Fdispatched a trauma team in a car from
OL,19,FLondon's Air Ambulance.
OL,26,@pD@TOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782911913
OL,3,CBoy, 13, who died at Royal Victoria
OL,4,CDock 'was retrieving football from
OL,5,Cwater'
OL,7,F"Very sadly, despite the best efforts
OL,8,Fof our crews, a child was pronounced
OL,9,Fdead at the scene."
OL,11,FThe death of the boy brings the number
OL,12,Fof people who have died in water-
OL,13,Frelated incidents during the recent
OL,14,Fhot weather to nine, and is in
OL,15,Faddition to the 15 who died during the
OL,16,Fspell of extremely warm weather in May.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/9
